# 2. 予兆

Len & Miku: What...?
Rin: Is that true, Kanade?
Kanade: Yes...
Kanade: Mafuyu sent us a message yesterday saying that she'll be taking a break from N25.
Ena & Mizuki: ...
Len: What do you think's going on...?
Luka: She had her synthesizer and computer taken away the other day, so something may have happened...
Miku: Did Mafuyu say anything else...?
Mizuki: She said her test scores are starting to slip... She apparently thinks she needs to focus on studying in order to keep her mom from worrying even more.
MEIKO: Focus on studying...
Mizuki: Do you guys think her mom's at it again...?
Mizuki: I mean, we haven't heard many details other than this.
Ena: Ugh... After we told her to let us know if something happens...
Len: I'm really worried...
Miku: ...
Miku: I'm going to see how she's doing...
Miku: If she is in pain, I want to be by her side...
Kanade: Miku...
Kanade: Yes, you're right. I'm sure she'll feel much better knowing you're there for her...
Ena: Please tell us if you hear anything. We want to help if we can too.
Miku: Okay.
Miku: But I'll go tomorrow since she is probably already asleep...
Miku: I'll be sure to let you all know if I do hear anything.
Kanade: Thank you, Miku...
KAITO: ...
Len: <So, this is Mafuyu's school...?>
Luka: <Yes, and it certainly seems like a fun place to be a student.>
Rin: <More importantly... Luka, why'd you follow us?>
Luka: <Oh, there's no need to be so apprehensive.>
Luka: <I'm worried about Mafuyu. Just like all of you.>
Rin: <If you say so...>
???: Here are the worksheets you asked for.
Rin: <That voice...>
Rin: <Mafuyu...?>
Teacher: Thank you, Asahina. I really appreciate the help.
Mafuyu: No, I was just fulfilling my duties as a class representative.
Mafuyu: Anyway, if you'll excuse me.
Len: <She doesn't sound like her usual self...>
Luka: <Oh, this is rather intriguing. I'm glad I decided to follow all of you here♪>
Rin: <Luka...>
Mafuyu: *Sigh*
Mafuyu: (Things are finally calm. I need to hurry and start today's portion.)
Mafuyu: Starting with...
???: <Mafuyu...>
Mafuyu: Huh...?
Mafuyu: What are you all doing here?
Miku: <Kanade and the others were worried about you.>
Mafuyu: Oh...
Mafuyu: I see...
Rin: <So, Mafuyu... Kanade told us that you needed to focus more on studying...>
Rin: <Is this because of something your mom said...?>
Mafuyu: No, it's not her... It's...my own fault...
Len: <It is?>
Mafuyu: Yes...
Mafuyu: Like I told Kanade and the others, I didn't do very well on my finals... That's why I need to do something to make sure my mom doesn't start worrying even more about me.
Mafuyu: So that I can also keep making music with N25...
Miku: <Oh...>
Mafuyu: Sorry, but I need to study. Thank you for coming to see me...
Miku: <That's okay...>
Miku: <Um, Mafuyu? Would you mind if I stayed with you for a bit?>
Mafuyu: Okay...
Mafuyu: (Next is calculus... These problems are usually fairly straightforward as long as you know what to do...)
Mafuyu: (Okay, I'm done... But that took longer than expected...)
Mafuyu: (If I don't work faster, I won't be able to check over my solutions during tests.)
Mafuyu: (I need to keep practicing these kinds of problems until I know them like the back of my hand...)
Mafuyu: (So that I can do better next time...)
Mafuyu: ...!
Mafuyu: (No, stay focused...)
Rin: (Mafuyu...)
Len: (We probably shouldn't interrupt her, but...)
Miku: (She looks like she's in so much pain...)
Luka: <Um, Mafuyu? How about you take a short break?>
Mafuyu: ...
Luka: <What if you went to talk to Kanade and the others? They've been waiting very patiently for you.>
Mafuyu: To see them...?
Mafuyu: No, I can't...
Mafuyu: I have to study... I have to...
Luka: <I see. I still don't quite fully understand, but studying must be very important to you, Mafuyu.>
Luka: <But in your current state, I feel that you won't be all that productive.>
Mafuyu: What...?
Luka: <As far as I can tell, you haven't been able to concentrate on your work. Doesn't that mean you should do something else instead?>
Mafuyu: Something else...?
Luka: <Yes. To take your mind off of school. To clear your head...>
Luka: <Isn't it important to do that from time to time?>
Mafuyu: But...
Mafuyu: ...
Mafuyu: I...
